---
import Layout from '../../components/Layout.astro';
const BASE = __BASE_PATH__;
---
<Layout title="都市传说" currentNav="urban-legend">
  <div class="breadcrumb"><a href={`${BASE}home/`} target="_blank">首页</a><span>›</span>都市传说</div>
  <h2>🌃 都市传说</h2>
  <p class="text-muted">每个城市都有它的秘密。本板块收集全国各地的都市传说、民间怪谈和街头流言。注意：内容未经核实，仅供娱乐。</p>
  <hr />
  <div class="post-item"><span class="tag tag-legend">北京</span> <a href={`${BASE}urban-legend/legend-001/`} target="_blank"><strong>朝内81号：京城第一凶宅</strong></a> <span class="text-muted">更新于 2026-01-10</span></div>
  <div class="post-item"><span class="tag tag-legend">上海</span> <a href={`${BASE}urban-legend/legend-002/`} target="_blank"><strong>延安路高架龙柱传说</strong></a> <span class="text-muted">更新于 2026-02-22</span></div>
  <div class="post-item"><span class="tag tag-legend">重庆</span> <a href={`${BASE}urban-legend/legend-003/`} target="_blank"><strong>红旗河沟地下迷宫传闻</strong></a> <span class="text-muted">更新于 2025-12-08</span></div>
  <p class="text-muted mt-2">有新的都市传说线索？欢迎<a href={`${BASE}submit/`} target="_blank">投稿</a>。</p>
</Layout>
